{"id": "art-402", "label": "Art. 402", "title": "Art. 402: Pronunţarea hotărârii", "slug": "art-402", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_696732340\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1269\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_696732340\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 402:\nPronun&#355;area hot&#259;rârii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1191458445\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1268\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1191458445\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Hot&#259;rârea se poate pronun&#355;a în\n&#351;edin&#355;&#259; public&#259;, la locul unde s-au desf&#259;&#351;urat\ndezbaterile, de c&#259;tre pre&#351;edinte sau de c&#259;tre un judec&#259;tor,\nmembru al completului de judecat&#259;, care va citi minuta, indicând &#351;i\ncalea de atac ce poate fi folosit&#259; împotriva hot&#259;rârii sau se poate\npronun&#355;a prin punerea solu&#355;iei la dispozi&#355;ia p&#259;r&#355;ilor\nde c&#259;tre grefa instan&#355;ei.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}